commit.message: Do not crash on missing fonts
Add flake.nix for building with Nix.

Added adaptive brightness functionality

Un-hard-code the lookup table & minor fixes

Minor fix: clamp the brightness value down so that it does not exceed max
Do not fail if config is not present in /etc
Use inotify for config change notifications
Update touchbar active layer in real time as conf is modified
Try to display an on-screen message if something went wrong
Remove unused variable "fb_info" and the function to get it
Fix config file help, remove stray dbg

Redraw only the buttons whose states changed and provide damage
information to the kernel

Use separate variables for the height and stride

The button height calculation is adjusted accordingly.
Don't assume that c_char is u8
Don't reserve space for pixel shifting when it is disabled
Fix y-shift, and shift getting stuck at the end
